FBIS3-14591 "drnes060_k_94001" FBIS-NES-94-060 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Mar 1994 IRAQ Defense Minister Wounded in Assassination Attempt NC2803174194 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan in Arabic 1500 GMT 28 Mar 94 NC2803174194 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan in Arabic 1500 GMT 28 Mar 94 Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] AL-MU'TAMAR newspaper, mouthpiece of the Unified Iraqi National Congress, has reported that the Free Revolutionary Officers Movement has issued a statement saying that the Iraqi regime's defense minister, 'Ali Hasan al-Majid, was the target of an assassination attempt in March. The paper cites the statement as saying that members of the Revolutionary Officers Movement opened fire at al-Majid outside his house in Baghdad, wounding him in the leg and arm and killing his bodyguard Major Salih and two other guards.
